data.description: Pride in ownership glistens from this home! From the amazing front door to the 2-story foyer w/lighted niche to the soaring great room ceiling, this one will be hard to pass up. It boasts 5 bedrooms w/the primary on the main level.  This home is made for entertaining featuring rec room(pool table, accessories and pool table light remain), wet bar(ref and freezer remaining) and family room with stone fireplace. For outdoor entertaining, it has a huge covered deck, concrete patio at the walk out basement door and lovely back yard. Need some excercise? The John Cox Pirtle Trail Greenbelt at Freeman Lake Park is right across the street! Amazing home...amazing location.  Don't wait. Schedule your tour today!!!
